span.span: Teachers will be contacting students via their school email.
Packets and supplies available in cabinets in front of the school.
Any updates will be communicated using email, robo-calls, website, and Facebook.

The following employee has been designated to handle questions and complaints of alleged discrimination: Title IX Coordinator, Civil Rights Coordinator, Andrew M. Perkins, Superintendent, (509) 964-7103, PO Box 150, 10831 N Thorp Hwy, Thorp, WA, 98946, perkinsa@thorpschools.org.
